casebody.data:
Beshara, Exr., Appellant, v. Schindler; ATD Corporation, Appellee.

[Cite as Beshara v. Schindler (1995), 74 Ohio St.3d 1209.]

*1210(No. 94-1424 Submitted October 10, 1995 Decided November 22, 1995.) McCarthy, Palmer, Volkema, Boyd & Thomas and Daniel R. Volkema, for appellant. Davis & Young Co., L.P.A., Gregory H. Collins and Martin J. Murphy, for appellee.

The appeal is dismissed, sua sponte, as having been improvidently allowed.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney and Bowman, JJ., concur. Pfeifer, J., dissents and would affirm the judgment of the court of appeals. Donna Bowman, J., of the Tenth Appellate District, sitting for Cook, J.
